79
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,400
Come out now.

80
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,580
Shen Zhiyi.

81
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,260
Don't hide inside.

82
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,120
Open the door.

83
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,880
Come out here.

84
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,720
I know you're in there.

85
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,040
Open up.

86
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,000
Shen Zhiyi.

87
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:55,440
Shen Zhiyi.

88
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:58,600
