94
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:08,180
Don't you know your brother is getting married?

95
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,480
500,000.

96
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,520
500,000 is not enough.

97
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:13,120
That little brat needs to pay the down payment.

98
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,770
I came here this time

99
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,920
to ask you for

100
