your brother's bride price money.

101
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,320
He's your son,

102
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,320
not mine.

103
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,440
Why should I pay for his bride price?

104
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,370
The eldest sister is like a mother.

105
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,770
Don't try to deny it.

106
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:27,760
Give me the money.

107
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,840
No matter what,

108
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:33,040
He is Zhiyi's father.

109
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,260
I'm also doing this for Zhiyi's sake.

110
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,000
as long as she doesn't get rid of that bloodsucker,

111
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,800
she won't have a single good day.

112
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,760
Bloodsucker?

113
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,200
What are you talking about?

114
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,260
What bloodsucker?

115
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,920
Zhiyi's father is causing trouble again.

116
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,050
Why is he here again?

117
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,720
Zhiyi is really pitiful.

118
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,760
This can't go on like this.

119
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,250
Jiang Cheng,

120
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,560
this time, for Zhiyi,

121
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,240
I really need to ask for your help.

122
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:57,680
Me?

123
00:05:59,200 --> 00:05:59,930
Jiang Cheng,

124
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:02,250
are you truly sincere about Zhiyi?

125
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:04,250
I won't give you any more money.

126
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,120
No way.

127
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:08,140
