128
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,170
You've barely achieved anything,

129
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,880
and now you're disowning me?

130
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:12,720
Unacceptable.

131
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,240
Only my mother raised me.

132
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,520
What have you ever done for me as a father?

133
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,850
A money-losing burden.

134
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,480
You still want love and care?

135
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,620
You're just like your mother.

136
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,640
Don't you dare talk about my mother.

137
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,260
If you don't leave now,

138
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,280
I'll call the police.

139
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:26,880
What?

140
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,280
You ungrateful girl!

141
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,340
What are you doing?

142
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,560
I admit I went a bit too far last time.

143
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:35,600
I'm afraid she might hate me.

144
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,480
Are you stupid?

145
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,200
If she really hated you,

146
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,730
would she let you stay here?

147
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:49,440
You've grown so capable you don't even recognize your own father.

148
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,080
Look at me.

149
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:52,960
Try that again.

150
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,480
Zhi Yi, are you alright?

151
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,120
Look at your miserable state.

152
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,980
Who are you putting on this life-and-death act for?

153
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,400
After this slap,

154
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,880
I'll no longer owe you anything.

155
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,900
From now on, we're strangers.

156
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:11,920
What?

157
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,020
Come back here!

158
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,320
Zhiyi, what's wrong?

159
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,040
Did he hit you?

160
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,080
What?

161
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,160
Do you want a slap too?

162
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:21,920
Look at me.

163
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,450
I'll fight you to the death!

164
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,770
Shen Jianjun, don't go too far!

165
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:30,260
I'm warning you, don't touch my friends!

166
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,970
You little brat.

167
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,200
You've recovered from your illness, huh?

168
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:37,330
How dare you push me?

169
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,280
I'll teach you a lesson.

170
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:39,920
Enough!

171
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,360
All these years,

172
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,600
I've been trying so hard to escape.

173
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:50,960
Everything I've done was to forget the pain you caused me.

174
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:54,320
I've finally managed to run this far away.

175
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,050
I have my own family now.

176
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,680
I thought I could finally

177
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:01,840
live like a normal person at last.

178
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,560
If you dare to cause trouble here again,

179
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:10,520
I'll call the police and have you arrested.

180
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,320
You dare to call the police on me?

181
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,820
I'll beat you to death!

182
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:14,840
Dad,

183
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,840
I really

184
