187
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:31,360
Come back!

188
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,220
Come back here!

189
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,120
Get back here!

190
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,360
I see you're Zhi Yi's father.

191
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,690
I won't lay a hand on you,

192
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,919
but I advise you to behave yourself.

193
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,370
What do you want?

194
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:45,080
You're not allowed to bully Zhi Yi anymore.

195
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:45,600
Zhi Yi!

196
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,560
You just wait!

197
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,930
I won't let you off the hook!

198
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,960
Get out of here, quick!

199
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,490
Get lost!

200
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,560
Leave now!

201
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,440
Hurry up and go!

202
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,820
Get out of here, quick!

203
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,450
Thank you all for today.

204
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,400
Don't mention it.

205
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,240
If you need anything in the future,

206
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:05,960
