211
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:11,520
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

212
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,120
Goodbye.

213
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,080
Bye-bye.

214
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,880
